description.narrative: Comprehensive Family and Child Support Unit (CFCSU) at Primary Health Care is integrated into the revised structure of PHC that provides an opportunity to establish the full -scale implementation of EDEI. Also, within the MTWG, Clinical Protocol for development monitoring of Children with Down Syndrome and Clinical Protocol for Children with Autism at PHC level were developed, WHO feedbacks were received and submitted for the approval by MoHSPP. UNICEF Tajikistan in collaboration with the MOHSPP contextualized the Bebbo Mobile Parenting Application for parents, caregivers, family doctors and nurses to promote nurturing care of children from 0- 6 years. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:20/01/2022
